  Missing media-video/mjpegtools RDEPEND used for mplexing during authoring.
  Thanks to "kisak" from Freenode for pointing it out.

  29 Jul 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> -dvdstyler-2.4.1.ebuild,
  -dvdstyler-2.5.1.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  old

*dvdstyler-2.7.2 (29 Jul 2014)

  29 Jul 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> +dvdstyler-2.7.2.ebuild:
  Version bump wrt #498904 by Paolo Pedroni. Pull in recent enough
  virtual/ffmpeg wrt #495088 by Cecil Curry. Punt USE="deprecated" and
  obsolete GNOME 2.x libgnomeui-2 library dependency with it wrt #508854.

*dvdstyler-2.5.1 (12 Aug 2013)

  12 Aug 2013; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> +dvdstyler-2.5.1.ebuild:
  Version bump, bug #472498. Fixes build with ffmpeg 2, bug #479390.

  01 Mar 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> -dvdstyler-2.1.ebuild,
  -dvdstyler-2.3.4.ebuild:
  old

*dvdstyler-2.4.1 (01 Mar 2013)

  01 Mar 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> +dvdstyler-2.4.1.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Version bump wrt #445544 by Fabio Bonfante. Validate dvdstyler.desktop and
  change USE="gnome" to USE="deprecated" since libgnomeui-2 is very old and not
  something we want by default for anyone. Rename USE="kernel_linux" to
  USE="udev" for eg. mdev users.

  11 Dec 2012; Ian Stakenvicius <axs@gentoo.org> dvdstyler-2.1.ebuild,
  dvdstyler-2.3.4.ebuild:
  virtualize the udev dependency

